40歲50歲呀叔上晒岸又嫌悶想打工 做呢d應該做到死都唔想走"},{"pid":"90884c3be92637b10275e738a811801158644dba","tid":1004762,"uid":195449,"like":411,"dislike":0,"score":411,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T05:55:55.000Z","msg":"重點確實改善到業績亦到生存到而家<br />\n返工開心已經贏其他7成又無錢又唔開心既公司<br />\n剩低3成係比到錢放棄開心舒服既公司<br />\n流失率低又有競爭力已經值得其他公司學習<br />\n成日羨慕外國公司好，而家香港有例子就不斷搵位入去攻擊又話做假又唔放假又剩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗拿大假去旅行放鬆已經證明份工好做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4fbf718244e8cd82cc0f6fd6dfcd16ad154b949","tid":1004762,"uid":62815,"like":171,"dislike":1,"score":170,"quote":{"pid":"fbc793d2b33e53186297e077b9f78e9eb8b4e902","tid":1004762,"uid":51920,"like":4,"dislike":44,"score":-40,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T19:03:06.000Z","msg":"搞咁多野 不如加人工好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T06:02:30.000Z","msg":"管理學嚟講<br />\n加人工只會令人返工<br />\n唔會令人想返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8673ee4d112b65f05a113494e276b43677229628","tid":1004762,"uid":92064,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T06:03:56.000Z","msg":"AL都唔請，痴撚線公司"},{"pid":"2dfdeafe795b7e3af63538e6155249dc6a9fb00d","tid":1004762,"uid":50801,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T06:40:54.000Z","msg":"返工舒服就已經唔需要加太多錢留人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e01e3c147c5bbc70ee3771d25b703c07d2a6b5","tid":1004762,"uid":38472,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T06:47:25.000Z","msg":"講真，做得開心，邊個人會想走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b616367f38dd24fb715ebe3c13f5085674184d","tid":1004762,"uid":189417,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T06:47:45.000Z","msg":"返工舒服佢都有份嘆<br />\n員工關係亦都好<br />\n醒既"},{"pid":"20a7ff6a98eb4d3fc61aac809b0675e9a9e37e59","tid":1004762,"uid":13936,"like":1,"dislike":